    "Adicione no Info.plist do app as chaves NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription e NSMicrophoneUsageDescription para usar comandos de voz no Modo Cozinha." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Add the NSSpeechRecognitionUsageDescription and NSMicrophoneUsageDescription keys to the app's Info.plist to use voice commands in Cooking Mode." } },
